query:
SELECT 
  sourceType,
  COUNT(*) as total,
  SUM(CASE WHEN sourceUrl IS NOT NULL AND sourceUrl != '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as with_url,
  SUM(CASE WHEN sourceUrl IS NULL OR sourceUrl = '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as without_url,
  ROUND(100.0 * SUM(CASE WHEN sourceUrl IS NOT NULL AND sourceUrl != '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / COUNT(*), 1) as percent_with_url
FROM properties 
GROUP BY sourceType
ORDER BY total DESC;
